The Truth Behind the Bargain Dog Trade

Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Jonathan Maitland, published by ITV broadcasted as part of ITV Tonight series in 2014 - English narration


Information
------------------------------

The Truth Behind the Bargain Dog Trade
There are more pet dogs in the UK than ever before, with tens of thousands of puppies going on sale every year. But has this led to an increase in unhealthy animals? Jonathan Maitland investigates the multimillion-pound puppy-breeding business, revealing how the demand for `designer dogs' has led to inhumane breeding conditions. He also finds out whether the rules about keeping animals safe are being enforced, and tracks down the European dealers willing to risk puppies' lives by smuggling them into the UK

